          "plain_text": "Mindful states of mind don’t really last all that long for me. They come and go. I still get lost in thoughts and completely wrapped up in emotions. Yet through practice, I’ve noticed that the periods of mindfulness have become more frequent, and longer in duration. ",
          "href": null
        }
