            "content": "Then, once you begin to clearly see your reactions through a state of mindfulness. You will become aware of certain reactions that you don’t agree with, reactions that you do not want to continue. Slowly at first, but faster as mindfulness grows, your mind will sense these reactions about to occur and react differently. Be intentional about the kind of reactions that you wish to cultivate and congratulate your mind when it chooses them. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "Then, once you begin to clearly see your reactions through a state of mindfulness. You will become aware of certain reactions that you don’t agree with, reactions that you do not want to continue. Slowly at first, but faster as mindfulness grows, your mind will sense these reactions about to occur and react differently. Be intentional about the kind of reactions that you wish to cultivate and congratulate your mind when it chooses them. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
